        BINEPS_FONT - Include font into Binary EPS file? YES or NO@{par}
        BINEPS_DPI - x and y dpi of the preview seperated by a 'x'@{par}
        IFF_DPI - x and y dpi seperated by a 'x'@{par}
        TIFF_DPI - x and y dpi seperated by a 'x'@{par}
        PROMPT - If this argument is specified, all other arguments are ignored
and the @{"Settings Window" link setwin} will be opened@{par}
  @{b}result:@{ub} value corresponding to ITEM@{par}

